s directory, and use blog: false in your Docusaurus config.","s":"Welcome","u":"/open-source-web/zh/blog/welcome","h":"","p":85},{"i":88,"t":"Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet... ...consectetur adipiscing elit. Pellentesque elementum dignissim ultricies. Fusce rhoncus ipsum tempor eros aliquam consequat. Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet","s":"First Blog Post","u":"/open-source-web/zh/blog/first-blog-post","h":"","p":87},{"i":90,"t":"Changelog_Blog","s":"index","u":"/open-source-web/zh/docs/Changelog_Blog/","h":"","p":89},{"i":93,"t":"ChangelogBlogSidebar","s":"index","u":"/open-source-web/zh/docs/Changelog_Blog/Blog/","h":"","p":92},{"i":95,"t":"ChangelogBlogSidebar","s":"index","u":"/open-source-web/zh/docs/Changelog_Blog/Changelog/","h":"","p":94},{"i":98,"t":"你准备好为你的开源项目创建文档网站了吗？","s":"来自 Docusaurus 的问候","u":"/open-source-web/zh/docs/greeting","h":"#来自-docusaurus-的问候","p":96},{"i":100,"t":"会显示在右上方的目录 这样，你的用户不用通读全文就可以知晓这篇文章的主要内容。","s":"标题","u":"/open-source-web/zh/docs/greeting","h":"#标题","p":96},{"i":102,"t":"你可以在每个文档或主题配置中设置目录包含的标题层级。 标题会保持恰当的间距，让文章看起来层级清晰。 列表可以帮助您 阐述关键点 使读者记忆深刻 并且您可以将它们 嵌套多次","s":"目录默认只包括 h2 和 h3 标题。","u":"/open-source-web/zh/docs/greeting","h":"#目录默认只包括-h2-和-h3-标题","p":96},{"i":104,"t":"home_2","s":"home_2","u":"/open-source-web/zh/docs/Home/home_2","h":"","p":103},{"i":106,"t":"home_1","s":"home_1","u":"/open-source-web/zh/docs/Home/home_1","h":"","p":105},{"i":108,"t":"Let's discover Docusaurus in less than 5 minutes.","s":"Tutorial Intro","u":"/open-source-web/zh/docs/intro","h":"","p":107},{"i":110,"t":"Get started by creating a new site. Or try Docusaurus immediately with docusaurus.new.","s":"Getting Started","u":"/open-source-web/zh/docs/intro","h":"#getting-started","p":107},{"i":112,"t":"Node.js version 18.0 or above: When installing Node.js, you are recommended to check all checkboxes related to dependencies.","s":"What you'll need","u":"/open-source-web/zh/docs/intro","h":"#what-youll-need","p":107},{"i":114,"t":"Generate a new Docusaurus site using the classic template. The classic template will automatically be added to your project after you run the command: npm init docusaurus@latest my-website classic You can type this command into Command Prompt, Powershell, Terminal, or any other integrated terminal of your code editor. The command also installs all necessary dependencies you need to run Docusaurus.","s":"Generate a new site","u":"/open-source-web/zh/docs/intro","h":"#generate-a-new-site","p":107},{"i":116,"t":"Run the development server: cd my-website npm run start The cd command changes the directory you're working with. In order to work with your newly created Docusaurus site, you'll need to navigate the terminal there. The npm run start command builds your website locally and serves it through a development server, ready for you to view at http://localhost:3000/. Open docs/intro.md (this page) and edit some lines: the site reloads automatically and displays your changes.","s":"Start your site","u":"/open-source-web/zh/docs/intro","h":"#start-your-site","p":107},{"i":118,"t":"QuickStart","s":"index","u":"/open-source-web/zh/docs/QuickStart/","h":"","p":117},{"i":120,"t":"APP","s":"index","u":"/open-source-web/zh/docs/TechnicalDocs/APP/","h":"","p":119},{"i":122,"t":"TechnicalDocs","s":"index","u":"/open-source-web/zh/docs/TechnicalDocs/","h":"","p":121},{"i":124,"t":"FirmWare","s":"index","u":"/open-source-web/zh/docs/TechnicalDocs/FirmWare/","h":"","p":123},{"i":126,"t":"HardWare","s":"index","u":"/open-source-web/zh/docs/TechnicalDocs/HardWare/","h":"","p":125},{"i":128,"t":"asdasdasdasd","s":"nihao","u":"/open-source-web/zh/docs/TechnicalDocs/HardWare/nihao","h":"","p":127}],"index":{"version":"2.3.9","fields":["t"],"fieldVectors":[["t/67",[0,2.308,1,1.643,2,2.308,3,1.643,4,2.67,5,1.643,6,1.643,7,1.643,8,1.643,9,1.643,10,1.643,11,1.823,12,1.823,13,1.03,14,1.823,15,1.823,16,1.823,17,1.823,18,1.823,19,1.823,20,1.823,21,1.643,22,1.823,23,1.823]],["t/69",[0,2.675,1,1.904,2,2.675,3,1.904,5,1.904,6,